Name: Home Run Solitaire
About the game: Here we are, another nerve-racking baseball season is just around the corner and the Solitaire Strikers are ready to claim the victory. Are you good enough to join the team and bring the Strikers to the top of the league? Impress your coach and solve 20 levels of non-stop solitaire fun. Aim for the home run and finish this season as MVP! A store packed with Baseball items 20 levels to play Mini-games 180 innings to complete Relaxing music Full Voice Over
